1
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:11,000
I already have someone in mind

2
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:16,160
The Fifth Concubine is already another man's wife

3
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:18,720
Why can't you let her go? Why bother?

4
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:22,560
Who knew Master Ai knew feng shui

5
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,800
and gossip so well too

6
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,760
The cart has already gone far

7
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,120
Hurry and help me carry this

8
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,200
Wait for me

9
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,160
Master, more and more villagers have the plague

10
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,640
We don't have enough cimicifuga left

11
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,280
Got it

12
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,440
Go make a pot of tea

13
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:18,280
Master Jiang

14
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,520
That day, you said Li Zhong's wronged spirit kills

15
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,960
You were joking with me

16
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,520
Just trying to scare me, right?

17
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:28,080
You saw those sparks falling to the ground too

18
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,960
Don't forget

19
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:33,880
Back then, Li Zhong was burned with the paper effigy

20
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,880
Now the paper effigy is haunting us

21
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:39,920
It is clearly possessed by Li Zhong's spirit

22
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,840
It's all my fault for being careless

23
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,440
Burning the effigy drew in his wronged spirit

24
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,200
What do we do now, what do we do?

25
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:55,320
After Li Zhong died, his body lay in the wild for years

26
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,840
With no one to bury him

27
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,600
So his resentment could not fade

28
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,680
Is there any way to break it?

29
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,280
This wronged spirit is very fierce

30
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,880
If it is to be suppressed

31
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,560
It will cost this poor Taoist ten years of life

32
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,560
No, no

33
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,640
Master Jiang

34
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,560
You can't do that

35
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,760
You have to find a way to save my life

36
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:17,160
As long as Li Zhong's resentment can be eased

37
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,560
Any amount you want is fine

38
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,360
Name your price

39
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,360
Three hundred silver dollars

40
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,360
Fine, I will pay, I will pay

41
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,200
Three thousand silver dollars

42
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,000
Deal

43
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,840
Deal

44
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,480
Have some water, sister-in-law

45
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,200
If you're hungry, have some pastries

46
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,000
Have some fruit

47
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,480
He will be back soon

48
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:44,320
See? Isn't he back already?

49
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,480
You finally came back

50
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,520
The Fifth Concubine has waited for you all day

51
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,760
Fatty, I have not eaten all day

52
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,640
I am a little hungry

53
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,880
Go buy me something to eat

54
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,000
All right

55
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,160
Master Ai, Master Ai

56
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,160
Come on, let's go together

57
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,600
All right, let's go

58
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:10,640
This way

59
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:18,040
You came to my shop so late today

60
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,800
Aren't you afraid the servants will gossip?

61
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:31,920
My mother asked me to invite you to gather my father's bones

62
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:39,000
So Madam Zhao no longer finds me inauspicious now

63
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,760
Forget it if you are unwilling

64
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,360
My Zhao family did wrong by you first

65
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:52,160
The Wang family's Fifth Concubine is truly arrogant

66
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:56,040
Is that how you ask someone for help?

67
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,800
Let go of me

68
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,360
Leave Wang Shengchang

69
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,720
and I will help you

70
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,720
Wang Shengchang will be back in a few days

71
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,880
If he sees you acting so frivolously

72
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,160
He definitely will not spare you

73
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:16,280
Fine, then I will make it real between us

74
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:20,320
Let's see if Wang Shengchang divorces you then

75
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,440
Are you crazy?

76
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,840
Let go of me

77
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,080
I am crazy

78
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,320
I am sorry, Xu Nan

79
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:15,040
I only wanted you to leave Wang Shengchang soon

80
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:17,160
I did not mean to hurt you

81
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,880
I agree to what you just said

82
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,320
Then thank you, Mr. Zheng

83
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,000
How did it go?

84
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:47,320
I have already spoken with the heads of the five guilds

85
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,280
They will gather at your house tomorrow noon

86
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,160
To discuss raising this money

87
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,680
I have thought it through

88
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:55,640
Each guild will put up 800 silver dollars

89
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,600
Then we can clear a profit of 1000

90
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,800
You really do have a knack for this

91
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:08,360
What if those guilds do not cooperate?

92
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:12,000
That is because not enough people have died yet

93
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,240
Let a few more die

94
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,800
and those guild heads will be scared

95
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,360
Didn't you say you were better?

96
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,120
Almost better

97
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,080
Thanks to the medicinal bath from Master Jiang

98
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,800
All right, I am leaving the fundraising to you

99
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,000
Pay more attention, and put me at ease

100
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,200
I am leaving

101
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,400
Who is it?

102
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,680
Who's playing tricks here?

103
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:05,600
Come find me.

104
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,280
Get out here now!

105
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,440
I'm right here.

106
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,240
Where are you going?

107
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:32,360
A ghost! Help! Help!

108
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,760
A ghost! There's a ghost! Don't go, play with me.

109
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:39,120
A ghost! A ghost!

110
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:41,000
You mean me?

111
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,120
A ghost!

112
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,400
It's so late already.

113
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,360
Why isn't Secretary back yet?

114
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,440
Nothing happened, right?

115
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,880
It shouldn't have.

116
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,000
Sorry to keep you waiting.

117
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,960
There have been far too many patients lately.

118
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,120
My master,

119
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,800
he truly can't be everywhere at once.

120
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:08,360
so he sent me to discuss the ritual with you.

121
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,840
Young Shen, that's all right.

122
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,760
It's good that you came.

123
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:12,680
Sit down, sit down.

124
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,880
Don't stand on ceremony, Mayor.

125
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:18,040
This ritual will cost my master years of his life,

126
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,800
and he could suffer backlash as well.

127
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,320
Three thousand silver dollars

128
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,680
won't do, I'm afraid.

129
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,760
It has to be five thousand.

130
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,760
Five thousand?

131
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:32,320
No, this was agreed on before.

132
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,600
Y-you're raising the price on the spot.

133
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,480
I've been seeing doctors lately,

134
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,280
and it's cost me quite a lot.

135
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:42,640
Business at the firm has been poor these two years.

136
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,760
Even if it were good, I couldn't pay that much.

137
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:45,680
Exactly.

138
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,640
Mayor, this is money to buy your life.

139
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:54,560
If the paper effigy's curse falls on you,

140
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,160
then even money won't save you in time.

141
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,400
That matter was just an accident.

142
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,160
If it can, let that paper effigy come for me.

143
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,080
I'm not afraid.

144
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,840
Look, look! What is that?

145
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,360
Where did this paper effigy come from?

146
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,640
Who put this paper effigy here?

147
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,040
This is terribly unlucky.

148
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,360
Help!

149
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,320
Isn't that Secretary?

150
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:36,120
Put out the fire! Hurry, put it out!

151
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:43,400
Quick, quick, quick!
